1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,500
Previously on Breaking Bad...

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,200
You clearly don't know who you're talking to,
so let me clue you in.

3
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:13,400
I am not in danger, Skyler.
I am the danger.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,600
A guy opens his door and gets shot,
and you think that of me?

5
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:22,800
No. I am the one who knocks.

6
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,500
Chemistry is the study of matter,
but I prefer to see it as the study of change.

7
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,800
Electrons change their energy levels.
Molecules change their bonds.

8
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:38,200
Elements combine and change
into compounds.

9
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:43,600
But that's alright, that's life.
It's growth, then decay, then transformation.

10
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:47,800
It is fascinating, really.

11
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:53,000
Say my name.

12
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:57,400
You're Heisenberg.

13
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,500
You're goddamn right.
